{"name": "nonebot-plugin-pypistats", "metadata": {"name": "nonebot-plugin-pypistats", "version": "0.1.6", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["nonebot2", "nonebot-plugin-alconna", "httpx", "pyecharts", "nonebot-plugin-htmlrender", "nonebot-plugin-localstore"], "summary": "Default template for PDM package", "upload_time": 1734059279}, "documentation": ["<div align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://v2.nonebot.dev/store\"><img src=\"https://github.com/A-kirami/nonebot-plugin-template/blob/resources/nbp_logo.png\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" alt=\"NoneBotPluginLogo\"></a>\n  <br>\n  <p><img src=\"https://github.com/A-kirami/nonebot-plugin-template/blob/resources/NoneBotPlugin.svg\" width=\"240\" alt=\"NoneBotPluginText\"></p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n# nonebot-plugin-pypistats\n\n_\u2728 \u901a\u8fc7\u673a\u5668\u4eba\u67e5\u770bPyPi\u5305\u7684\u4e0b\u8f7d\u6b21\u6570 \u2728_\n\n</div>\n\n\u4e00\u4e2a\u901a\u8fc7nonebot\u4e0epypistats\u5bf9\u63a5\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684\u4e0b\u8f7d\u91cf\u67e5\u8be2\u63d2\u4ef6\n\n> [!IMPORTANT]\n> \u6570\u636e\u662f\u5426\u53ef\u4fe1\u8bf7\u81ea\u884c\u5224\u65ad\n\n\n## \ud83d\udcbf \u5b89\u88c5\n\n<details open>\n<summary>\u4f7f\u7528 nb-cli \u5b89\u88c5</summary>\n\u5728 nonebot2 \u9879\u76ee\u7684\u6839\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u6253\u5f00\u547d\u4ee4\u884c, \u8f93\u5165\u4ee5\u4e0b\u6307\u4ee4\u5373\u53ef\u5b89\u88c5\n\n    nb plugin install nonebot-plugin-pypistats\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>\u4f7f\u7528\u5305\u7ba1\u7406\u5668\u5b89\u88c5</summary>\n\u5728 nonebot2 \u9879\u76ee\u7684\u63d2\u4ef6\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b, \u6253\u5f00\u547d\u4ee4\u884c, \u6839\u636e\u4f60\u4f7f\u7528\u7684\u5305\u7ba1\u7406\u5668, \u8f93\u5165\u76f8\u5e94\u7684\u5b89\u88c5\u547d\u4ee4\n\n<details>\n<summary>pip</summary>\n\n    pip install nonebot-plugin-pypistats\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>pdm</summary>\n\n    pdm add nonebot-plugin-pypistats\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>poetry</summary>\n\n    poetry add nonebot-plugin-pypistats\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>conda</summary>\n\n    conda install nonebot-plugin-pypistats\n</details>\n\n\u6253\u5f00 nonebot2 \u9879\u76ee\u6839\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u7684 `pyproject.toml` \u6587\u4ef6, \u5728 `[tool.nonebot]` \u90e8\u5206\u8ffd\u52a0\u5199\u5165\n\n    plugins = [\"nonebot_plugin_pypistats\"]\n\n</details>\n\n## \ud83c\udf89 \u4f7f\u7528\n### \u6307\u4ee4\u8868\n| \u6307\u4ee4 | \u6743\u9650 | \u9700\u8981@ | \u8303\u56f4 | \u8bf4\u660e |\n|:-----:|:----:|:----:|:----:|:----:|\n| \u4e0b\u8f7d\u7edf\u8ba1 [\u5305\u540d] [\u7c7b\u578b] | all | \u5426 | all | \u7c7b\u578b\u9009\u9879\u6709p\uff1anonebot-plugin-\u548ca: nonebot-adapter-\u4e24\u79cd\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u4e0d\u5199\u53c2\u6570\u7684\u8bdd\u90a3\u5c31\u662f\u76f4\u63a5\u67e5\u8be2|\n\n### \u6307\u4ee4\u4f8b\u5b50\n\n<details>\n<summary>\u70b9\u51fb\u5c55\u5f00</summary>\n\n![\u56fe\u4e00](./img/stats1.png)\n![\u56fe\u4e8c](./img/stats2.png)\n\n</details>\n"], "modules": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_pypistats.uasge", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_pypistats.uasge.usage", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_pypistats", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_pypistats._", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "matcher", "type": {"name": "Matcher", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot.matcher.Matcher", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "name", "type": {"name": "Match", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot_plugin_alconna.Match", "project": "nonebot-plugin-alconna"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "nb", "type": {"name": "Match", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot_plugin_alconna.Match", "project": "nonebot-plugin-alconna"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, 